{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Menyambut Game Spider-Man PS4, Ini Dia Game Spider-Man Jaman Dulu!","content":"<p>Saat ini yang sedang <em>trending</em> di dunia <em>gaming</em> adalah <em>game</em> baru Spider-Man yang dirilis untuk PlayStation 4 secara ekslusif.</p>\n<p>Diberi judul “Marvel’s Spider-Man”, <em>game</em> aksi petualangan terbaru dari Peter Parker alias Spider-Man ini memang fenomenal. Gak hanya memiliki grafis yang super cakep (terutama saat dimainkan di <em>console</em> PlayStation 4 Pro), <em>game</em> ini juga seru dalam hal <em>gameplay</em>; walaupun ada pendapat yang mengatakan kalau <em>game</em> buatan <em>developer</em> Insomniac ini sedikit terlalu mirip <em>game-game</em> Batman Arkham <em>series</em>-nya <em>developer</em> Rocksteady.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51097\" style=\"width: 638px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51097\" data-attachment-id=\"51097\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/spider-man-ps4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-PS4.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"628,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Spider-Man PS4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spider-Man PS4 (Sumber: PlayStation.Com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-PS4-300x149.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-PS4.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51097\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-PS4.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Spiderman - Spider-Man PS4\" width=\"628\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-PS4.jpeg 628w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-PS4-300x149.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51097\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spider-Man PS4 (Sumber: PlayStation.Com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Game Spider-Man PS4 juga punya berbagai <em>‘easter egg’</em> alias bonus-bonus tersembunyi yang siap untuk ditemukan oleh <em>gamers</em>. Salah satu yang sudah ditemukan, namun bernuansa sedih, adalah proposal lamaran seorang <em>gamer</em> bernama Tyler Schultz kepada pacarnya Maddie.</p>\n<p>Saat game ini diluncurkan, Maddie rupanya sudah putus dengan Tyler dan memilih kakak Tyler sebagai pasangan. “Dia mutusin gue dan pergi dengan abang gue, melupakan kebersamaan kami selama lima tahun terakhir” curhat Tyler Schultz lewat video yang di-<em>upload</em> di YouTube.</p>\n<p><em>Video game</em> Spider-Man tentu saja sudah lama ada di dunia <em>game</em>. Malah<em> game</em> Spider-Man sudah pernah dirilis sejak era ‘80an (tepatnya 1982) lewat <em>console</em> jadul Atari 2600. Tentu saja jangan berharap grafis kinclong di <em>game</em> itu, karena gambarnya sangat sederhana sekali.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51098\" style=\"width: 266px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51098\" data-attachment-id=\"51098\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/spider-man-atari-2600-256x354/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256x354.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"256,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256&#215;354\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: PlayConsole&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256x354-246x300.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256x354.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51098\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256x354.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Superman - Atari\" width=\"256\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256x354.jpeg 256w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Spider-Man-Atari-2600-256x354-246x300.jpeg 246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51098\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">ATARI (Sumber gambar: PlayConsole)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-usbQDfTIqE\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Iklan Spider-Man Atari 2600</p>\n<p>“<em>Spider-Man: The Video Game”</em> dirilis tahun 1991 untuk <em>video game arcade</em> oleh Sega. Grafisnya keren untuk era ‘90an. Karena dirilis untuk <em>arcade</em>, <em>gameplay-</em>nya menganut sistem <em>‘co-op’</em> alias bekerja sama. Empat pemain dapat bermain sekaligus di <em>video game</em> ini. Karakter yang tersedia adalah Spider-Man, Black Cat, Namor the Sub-Mariner dan Hawkeye. <em>Gameplay</em>-nya berupa <em>‘side scrolling action adventure’</em> yang memang cocok dan sedang <em>booming</em> di berbagai <em>arcade center</em> dunia pada masa itu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51099\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51099\" data-attachment-id=\"51099\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"608,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spider-man the video game 1991 sega\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spider-man The Video Game 1991 Sega (Sumber gambar: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega-300x154.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51099\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Spiderman - Spider-man The Video Game 1991 Sega\" width=\"608\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega.jpeg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-the-video-game-1991-sega-300x154.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51099\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spider-man The Video Game 1991 Sega (Sumber gambar: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0_Y80vd0Qgk\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Video gameplay</em></p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga:</strong> <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/high-score-girl-anime-video-game-retro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">High Score Girl, Anime yang Mengulik Video Game Era 90an</a></p>\n<p>Saat peta <em>video game</em> dunia berubah arah dengan kelahiran <em>console</em> berkekuatan <em>arcade</em> (seperti Sony PlayStation dan Sega Saturn), <em>game-game</em> yang diciptakan cenderung menuju tampilan dan <em>gameplay</em>  3D dengan grafis <em>polygonal</em>. Hal ini merupakan perkembangan sistem dari <em>gameplay</em> 2D (pergerakan satu arah seperti misalnya Super Mario Bros) dengan grafis <em>hand-drawn </em>yang ada di <em>console</em> generasi sebelumnya seperti Super Nintendo dan Sega Genesis.</p>\n<p><em>Game-game</em> bertema Spider-Man ikut mengalami perubahan tersebut.</p>\n<p>“Spider-Man” (2000) buatan <em>developer</em> Neversoft untuk <em>console</em> PlayStation sering dianggap sebagai salah satu <em>game</em> Spider-Man era 3D terbaik yang pernah diciptakan. Satu hal menarik dari <em>game</em> yang di-<em>publish</em> oleh Activision ini adalah <em>gameplay</em> yang menggunakan <em>‘engine mechanic’</em> dari <em>game</em> sukses PlayStation lainnya: Tony Hawk’s Pro Skater (1999).</p>\n<p>Jika kamu pernah merasakan era ‘rental PS’, maka <em>game-game</em> ini hampir pasti pernah kamu mainkan selain <em>game-game</em> Winning Eleven / Pro Evolution Soccer.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51100\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51100\" data-attachment-id=\"51100\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/spider-man-ps1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-ps1.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"608,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spider-man ps1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spider-man PS 1 (Sumber: GamesGrabr)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-ps1-300x154.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-ps1.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51100\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-ps1.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Spiderman - Spiderman PS 1\" width=\"608\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-ps1.jpeg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-ps1-300x154.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51100\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spider-man PS 1 (Sumber: GamesGrabr)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga: </strong><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/winning-elevenpro-evolution-soccer-game-wajib-sejuta-umat-gamers-ps-indonesia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Winning Eleven/Pro Evolution Soccer: Game Wajib Sejuta Umat Gamers PS Indonesia</a></p>\n<p><em>Game</em> Spider-Man PS buatan Neversoft memiliki grafis yang keren banget (tentunya untuk ukuran jaman PlayStation). <em>Gameplay</em> tiga dimensi menjadikan <em>game</em> ini terasa lebih bebas dan luas ketimbang <em>game-game</em> Spider-Man sebelumnya yang menganut sistem petualangan 2D <em>side scrolling</em>. Di Spider-Man PS, kita beraksi seperti Spider-Man dalam komik. Melompat. Berayun. Menjelajahi New York seperti kisah dalam komik-komik Spider-Man. Semua dengan pergerakan bebas kesana-kemari dalam dunia 3D.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1yndr441-Wo\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Saking suksesnya <em>game</em> Spider-Man tadi, <em>game</em> itu di-<em>port</em> ke console lain juga. Seperti Sega Dreamcast dan Nintendo N64, di mana grafis yang ditampilkan jadi lebih bagus, karena keduanya memiliki kekuatan grafis lebih baik dari PlayStation.<em> Game</em> itu bahkan mendapatkan versi <em>Game Boy</em> juga. Tentunya dengan grafis diubah jadi 2D <em>side scrolling</em>.</p>\n<p>Sebuah kemunduran sih… Tapi ini <em>Game Boy.</em> Mesin yang tidak sanggup menangani grafis 3D seperti NDS.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51101\" style=\"width: 352px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51101\" data-attachment-id=\"51101\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/spider-man-gameboy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-gameboy.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"342,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spider-man gameboy\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spider-man Gameboy (Sumber: Amazon)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-gameboy-300x274.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-gameboy.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51101\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-gameboy.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Spiderman - Spiderman Gameboy\" width=\"342\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-gameboy.jpeg 342w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/spider-man-gameboy-300x274.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 342px) 100vw, 342px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51101\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spider-man Gameboy (Sumber: Amazon)</p></div></p>\n<p>Spider-Man tidak hanya muncul di <em>game</em> di mana dia menjadi tokoh utama.</p>\n<p>Di <em>game</em> “Marvel Ultimate Alliance” (2006) untuk PS2, PS3, Xbox, Xbox 360, Spidey menjadi salah satu karakter yang dapat dimainkan selain karakter-karakter Marvel Comics lain yang populer seperti Wolverine, Captain America, Thor hingga karakter seperti Ghost Rider. Genre yang digunakan di <em>game</em> ini adalah <em>‘action role-playing’</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51102\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51102\" data-attachment-id=\"51102\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/marvel-ultimate-alliance/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-ultimate-alliance.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"608,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"marvel ultimate alliance\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Marvel Ultimate Alliance (Sumber: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-ultimate-alliance-300x154.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-ultimate-alliance.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51102\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-ultimate-alliance.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Spiderman - Marvel Ultimate Alliance \" width=\"608\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-ultimate-alliance.jpeg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-ultimate-alliance-300x154.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51102\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Marvel Ultimate Alliance (Sumber: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Selain itu Spider-Man juga sering menjadi salah satu karakter yang dapat dimainkan di <em>game-game</em> <em>fighting arcade</em> keluaran Capcom.</p>\n<p>Sebut saja seperti “Marvel Super Heroes” (1995), “Marvel Super Heroes vs Street Fighter” (1997), “Marvel vs Capcom: Clash of Super Heroes” (1998), “Marvel vs Capcom 2: New Age of Heroes” (2000) dan “Marvel vs Capcom 3: Fate of Two Worlds” (2011) untuk console PlayStation 3 dan Xbox 360.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51103\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51103\" data-attachment-id=\"51103\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"608,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"marvel vs capcom 3 spiderman\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Marvel vs Capcom 3 (Sumber: Wikia)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman-300x154.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman.jpeg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51103\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman.jpeg\" alt=\"Game Spiderman - Marvel vs Capcom 3\" width=\"608\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman.jpeg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-vs-capcom-3-spiderman-300x154.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51103\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Marvel vs Capcom 3 (Sumber: Wikia)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di <em>game-game</em> tadi, Spider-Man bertarung dengan menggunakan kekuatan seperti yang terlihat di buku komik maupun di game-game petualangan sebelumnya. Seru untuk dimainkan bersama teman-teman.</p>\n<p><strong>Gameplay Spidey MvC 3</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hU3KTym4mmA\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><em>Game</em> Spider-Man juga ada untuk platform <em>mobile smartphone</em> seperti misalnya “Marvel Future Fight” (2015) dan “Spider-Man Unlimited” (2016). Seperti halnya game <em>mobile</em> lain, <em>game-game</em> Spider-Man untuk <em>smartphone</em> ini memiliki <em>gameplay</em> sederhana dengan grafis yang bagus untuk ukuran <em>smartphone</em>. Lumayan untuk iseng-iseng mengisi waktu luang dengan bermain<em> game smartphone.</em></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51104\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51104\" data-attachment-id=\"51104\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menyambut-game-spider-man-ps4-ini-dia-game-spider-man-jaman-dulu/attachment/marvel-future-fight/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-future-fight.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"608,312\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"marvel future fight\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Marvel Future Fight (Sumber: AminoApps)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-future-fight-300x154.jpeg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/marvel-future-fight.jpeg\" class=\"siz